Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是市宫行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界大财阀市宫集团的社长之子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是 天生的人生赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是保送进T大的大学生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从学费到公寓 完全自力 都没有依靠父母
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在为止自立的理由 是我们市宫家的家训
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不欠人 不求人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市宫家长子代代相传的领带上也写着市宫家的家训
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我现在一直遵守着这个家训
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在我也只靠自己活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 即使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有恩必报的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的小孩真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然被一群小孩抢去了我的裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不生气 就等于他们欠了我人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在这个时间 这里没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人的话 秀一下内裤又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你PP不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我好热
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 现在最重要的是把裤子拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人误会而大叫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如果没看错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还差三厘米就犯公然猥亵罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 怎么会 你弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了 我自己想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能够在这种地方欠下这种人情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点 只差一点 只差一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定决心的话一定可以拿的到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被告上法庭也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想看到PP的话 就别回头看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不欠人 不求人 为了继承财团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须用我自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再这样往上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要理我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能欠别人的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这样被养大的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一岁开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被教育万事要靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从三岁开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一岁的时候欠爸爸的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在来还给爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 还不快点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把玩具放嘴里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要弄坏琪琪 然后大哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了这么大劲才让他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后小学四五年级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有了自觉要继承家业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 你的橡皮掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的事自己可以处理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没话说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 被柱子压住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点 靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我要死在这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好腥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我嘴里面会有鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我该先道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你欠我人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这二十一年间 我坚持 不欠人 不求人 的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可现在 可现在为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这个女人救了一命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才潜水的时候顺便抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 刚才的事让我情绪很差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命恩人意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以后能吃到美味蛋糕 是多亏了这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能继承财团坐上社长的位子 也是多亏了这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以后的人生也多亏了这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无以为报 救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要怎么样才能还你人情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你全身湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下我回家拿毛巾给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 不用特意回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 对了 我把毛巾铺在地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用地板吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它就只有潜水服能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很穷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子一个人在这种地方很辛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样简直就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还人情的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在这种地方很难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河边又潮湿 又吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的女孩子会很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我前见天刚好去卖了点股票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就有八亿左右可以用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 就给你买房子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作礼物送你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 说出想要的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就可以还人情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很冷吧 住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊 现在我就好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是地球人 我是金星人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 因为我是金星人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇上个电波族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 如果这样的话 那她真是不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还有什么烦恼的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的什么都可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 报恩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了我的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个星球 帮助别人都是得回礼的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 住口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说你什么都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 否则我的哮喘会发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哮喘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压力引起的 市宫家的遗传病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 让我帮你吧 就当是救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我把人情还了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说个愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活的轻松点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是没有不想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和我谈恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不欠人 不求人 是市宫家绝对不能违背的家训
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然救命恩人这么希望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要我用性命回报也是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和我谈恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉 市宫行说到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是和自称金星人也好 电波族也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩人就是恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天开始要和这个女人谈恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之今天要先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那首先有件事情要决定一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想住在住宅还是别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个 我当然是回自己家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 真不知道她在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后见面怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天回家慢慢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枕头 给你用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 没有被子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有好多报纸可以给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能坚持到多冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 别死在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我要住在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 恋人就是要整天在一起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人之间的距离美也是恋爱的一部分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我大概一天看不到你就忘记你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽量多来看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天先回自己家里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才不是说我一个女孩子在这种地方很危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要就算了 那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 真正的爱情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会让恋人独自留在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的恋人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该住在习惯的地方比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说都是新居
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住别墅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别墅的话在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想被爱的话就要先爱对方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明她救了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还犹豫什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家 对 就当是搬家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样想的话就没什么犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是别墅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然视野很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过缺点就是地板太硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是睡觉的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要面对现实 要积极面对现实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是市宫集团的下任社长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在这里的话一定要有那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟村长打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是这段河的负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是村长吧 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打招呼是我的特长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以在这种地方沉沦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这里就不止这个女孩在住 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少应该比电波女好说话的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个村长是什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如特征
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有颜色不同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是外国人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像因为这个被周围人议论了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己就很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出身好 头脑好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说又长得好看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可谓完人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 也不会靠外表判断别人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上你是最好的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样的话就好说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在叫他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做声的话就这样谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 我还没心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始这个人在这里住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色的绿色的绿色的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非但不是外国人 更不像人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不能靠外表判断的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不是就这样的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了不管怎么样我也是河童
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认 现在在日本也很少见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃惊也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 我也是第一次看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次看到我的同伴的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不管怎么样的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被排斥的话一定 会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你脖子后面的皮肤了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你的皮肤了 不过是穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 因为我是河童才这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要人身攻击哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被骗了 这个人不是河童
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长是河童
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我是金星人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长的确是河童
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人都是电波族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 本来不想引起冲突的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就尽量给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,较量一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来里面都是水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 就是这样的身体构造啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上半身紧紧贴着了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我不陪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 吃惊会觉得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己套上去河童的衣服的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也只不过是披着人皮的葫芦干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以完全否定我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 我在怎么看都不是假扮的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不能分辨什么是真实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是那么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不到此为止呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坐那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说些正经点的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没想要掩饰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么搞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 什么也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已经打过招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去躺会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你还没有名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名字叫行 市宫行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个已经不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没我给你取的名字 你在这里生活不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说下我的名字是小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊 这是这个玩偶起的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么起这种名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年三班 接二连三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有不甘心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以自己的名字为傲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是救命恩人在遵守这里的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在这里生活的话就要遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我取名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么名字我也不会埋怨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好 你已经有在这里生活的觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你就叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命名 招兵买马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚自己给别人的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说不会埋怨的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这不是欺负我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少给个好听的候补啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本名字 请起个日本名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再给你想一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说要很帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少来个顺口的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你就叫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内定采用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 怎么样 果然不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然日本名字不太适合他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就叫 采用 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是叫招兵买马
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很过分啊 就这样的被子来睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个被子可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没问题 我行的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我也疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为这个被子就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这块布 完全不能盖住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个之前我还要问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我出去过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘技协会的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能听完别人说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有自信说不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也就是一天前跟你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天说过这样的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.88,0:22:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 想起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:22:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只记得这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:22:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的恋人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是记得还是不记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.91,0:23:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.84,0:23:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 你说被子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有了 我本来就只有一条被子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上昨天那条就有两条
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那昨天小珊把唯一的被子给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有好多报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又欠了人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.03,0:23:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 哮喘又发了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.53,0:23:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 错的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.97,0:23:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊怎么会有两条被子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我看看你屋子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.20,0:23:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能理解 她平时是怎么生活的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹅绒大床
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.11,0:24:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又柔软又有弹性 哪国国王睡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.84,0:24:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希腊的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.64,0:24:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.82,0:24:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是希腊人丢在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.05,0:24:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.27,0:24:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长说的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.69,0:24:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是骗人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.38,0:24:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骗了 完全被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.66,0:24:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在外面超硬的地方要冷死的时候她就在这里享受
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.19,0:24:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了没
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.56,0:24:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人的幸福就是你的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.56,0:24:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.72,0:24:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这个人是电波族
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.73,0:24:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.22,0:25:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这样真太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.25,0:25:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没让恩人着凉太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.90,0:25:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枕头就这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.75,0:25:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还有捡到其他的枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.15,0:25:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个枕头村长说一年只能睡一次
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.14,0:25:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 已经不知道用了多少年了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.75,0:25:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个被子也是一起捡的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.51,0:25:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.72,0:25:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罩子 果然只是个罩子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.13,0:25:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之有点意外 你似乎过得还行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.24,0:25:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回家拿点必需品 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.49,0:25:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.10,0:25:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也再睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.62,0:25:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没有在中午之前醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.91,0:25:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间整理好了 给我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.72,0:25:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想看的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.80,0:25:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.74,0:26:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.41,0:26:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊其实也是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.79,0:26:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.57,0:26:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.74,0:26:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.77,0:26:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跑得很快 离开了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.46,0:26:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果为了不让眼泪流下而仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.06,0:26:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童对我说 眼睛会被灼伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.33,0:26:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招 多热你才会死
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.66,0:26:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的气温的话没事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.61,0:26:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的 能摸到太阳的气温吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.71,0:26:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 2BRIDGE
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.11,0:26:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种温度的话会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.52,0:26:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真脆弱
